ActCustoms Tariff
SubjectRegulations Amending the Regulations Defining “EU country or other CETA beneficiary”
PrecisRegulations Amending the REGULATIONS DEFINING "EU COUNTRY OR OTHER CETA BENEFICIARY" in order to remove the United Kingdom from the definition that specifies countries or territories that are considered Comprehensive and Economic Trade Agreement beneficiaries under Canada's Customs Tariff.
